Jack-O'Lantern (JACK)

Jack-O'Lantern themed probe cores in seven sizes.
All the modcons. Now with pumpkin chunking!

By zer0Kerbal, originally by @Porkjet

brought to you by KerbSimpleCo

Features

  • This addon adds seven sizes of Jack-O'Lantern shaped probe cores

Jack-O'-Lantern

by Porkjet.
Jack-O'Lantern themed probe cores in three sizes. All the modcons.

version 1.0.0.2 - ModCons

  • Spoiler

     

    • added tags.cfg patch
    • updated and modernized part.cfgs
    • moved parts from Utility to Pods
    • added Changelog.cfg
    • added CrewCapacity = 0
    • added explosionPotention = 0
    • added tags (using #autoloc_500345)
    • converted from PNG to DDS (DT5)
    • moved parts into JackOLantern/parts
    • moved patch(es) into JackOLantern/patches
    • added Readme.md
    • added .version file
    • added ControlPoint(s)
    • updated ModuleReactionWheel
    • added SASServiceLevel = 3
    • added ModuleDataTransmitter (5000)
    • adjusted ElectricChange per size
    • changed from ModuleLight to ModuleColorChanger

Three things learned while updating this mod:

    menuName = Decouple Bottom
  3. that ModuleDecouple can be srf 
    explosiveNodeID = srf
